The title of the issue (bug report) should have the version the bug was found on first.
Follow that with the character and location of the bug.
In the comment, give a short description of the bug and how the circumstances leading up to the bugs.
Finally, if possible, include a a file of a screenshot of the bug.

Example:
Title: 2.2.1 Raven Vault
Comment: The spank scene selection for Raven in the vault leads to nowhere and freezes the game. I had to
restart the game in order to unfreeze and continue.
Screenshot: (Imagine there's a file of a screenshot here)
